<tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><img border="0" src="../triangle.JPG"><font size="3" face="Tahoma" color="#004242"><b>SINGING SHORT SWORD</b></font></p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Class:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Bard</b></font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Minimum Level:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">50</font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Estimated Quest Length:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Over 30 hours</font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Quest NPC:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Baldric Slezaf</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Starting Zone:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Dreadlands&Comment=1">Dreadlands</a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Secondary Zones:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Karana, West&Comment=1">Karana, West</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Misty Thicket&Comment=1">Misty Thicket</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=South Ro&Comment=1">South Ro</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Lake Rathetear&Comment=1">Lake Rathetear</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Solusek A&Comment=1">Solusek A</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Unrest&Comment=1">Unrest</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Karana, South&Comment=1">Karana, South</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Skyfire Mountains&Comment=1">Skyfire Mountains</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Burning Woods&Comment=1">Burning Woods</a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Items Needed:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Top Part of Page 24</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Bottom Part of Page 24</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Page 25</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Chromodrac Guts</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Huge Onyx Drake Guts</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Red Wurm Guts</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Alluring Horn, Petrified Werewolf Skull</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Amygdalan Tendril, Backbone of an Ancient Fishman</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Large Red Dragon Scale, Large White Dragon Scale</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Trakanon Gut Strings</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Description:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>1.</b> This quest begins in the Dreadlands.  <b>Baldric Slezaf</b> will ask for 4 items: top part of page 24, bottom part of page 24, page 25, and a Lute made by Forpar Fizfla.
<br><br>
<b>2.</b> To get the <b>Top Part of Page 24</b>, you must go to West Karana and look for <b>Konia Swiftfoot</b>.  Talk to him and he will hand you a torch that you must take to <b>Fajio Knejo</b>.
<br><br>
<b>3.</b> You can find Fajio in Misty Thicket, near loc -250 -250.  Give him the torch and he will give you another torch to take to <b>Andad Filla</b>.
<br><br>
<b>4.</b> You can find Andad in South Ro near the Innothule Swamp zone.  Give him the torch and he will, once again, give you another torch to take to <b>Misty Tekchita</b>.
<br><br>
<b>5.</b> You can find Misty in Lake Rathetear.  She will be near the zone to the Arena.  Give her the torch and she will hand you <b>Misty's Ring</b>.
<br><br>
<b>6.</b> Return to West Karana and give Misty's Ring to <b>Konia</b>.  He will then reward you with the <b>Top Part of Page 24</b>.
<br><br>
<b>7.</b> One item down, still two to go.  To get the <b>Bottom Part of Page 24</b> you must talk to <b>Braenar Swiftfoot</b> in West Karana.  Ask him 'What doll?' and will give you an <b>Invoice</b>.
<br><br>
<b>8.</b> Head to Solusek A and give the Invoice to <b>Marfen Binkdirple</b>, the Gnome vendor at loc -300 -1080.  He will then give you the <b>Mechanical Doll</b>.
<br><br>
<b>9.</b> Head to Unrest and look for <b>Serra</b>.  She will be next to the Gnomish Spelunker at loc +700 -300.  Give her the Doll and she will a <b>Note for Braenar</b>.
<br><br>
<b>10.</b> Return to West Karana anf give the note to <b>Braenar</b>.  He will then give a <b>Note for Maligar</b>.
<br><br>
<b>11.</b> <b>Maligar</b> is also in West Karana.  Look for him at loc +1250 -10900.  Give him the Note and <b>Maligar's Enraged Doppleganger</b> will immediately spawn and attack you.  Kill this Doppleganger and loot the <b>Doppleganger's Head</b>.  Note that if Maligar is initially KOS to you, you will not be able to continue the quest unless you have an Enchanter charm Maligar so you can give him the Note.
<br><br>
<b>12.</b> Once you have the Doppleganger's Head, take it back to <b>Braenar</b>.  Give it to him and you will receive the <b>Mahlin's Bongos</b>.
<br><br>
<b>13.</b> Give the Bongos to <b>Konia Swiftfoot</b> and he will hand you the <b>Bottom Part of Page 24</b>.
<br><br>
<b>14.</b> Two more items to obtain.  To get <b>Page 25</b>, you must go to South Karana and talk to the Wood Elf Bard <b>Kelkin Mekia</b>.  She will ask you for 3 items: Chromodrac Guts, Red Wurm Guts, and Huge Onyx Drake Guts.
<br><br>
<b>15.</b> The <b>Chromodrac Guts</b> is dropped by a Chromodrac named <b>Edrik the Old</b>.  He spawns in Skyfire.  Kill him and loot his guts.
<br><br>
<b>16.</b> The <b>Red Wurm Guts</b> is dropped by a Wurm named <b>Nezekezena</b> in the Burning Woods.  Kill him and loot his guts.
<br><br>
<b>17.</b> The third and last guts, the <b>Huge Onyx Drake Guts</b> is dropped by a Drake in Rathe Mountains named <b>Blackwing</b>.  Kill him and loot his guts.
<br><br>
<b>18.</b> Return to South Karana and give <b>Kelkin</b> the 3 guts.  He will then reward you with <b>Page 25</b>.
<br><br>
<b>19.</b> One more item to obtain.  The last item is <b>Forpar's Lute</b>.  Head to the Ocean of Tears and look for Quag Maelstrom.  He spawns on Seafury Island, at loc +1530 -5810.  He is a level 45 Cyclops with roughly 9000 HPs.  Make sure you bring at least 2 groups to take him down.  He hits hard and will drain mana from players at a real fast rate.  Kill him and loot his <b>Alluring Horn</b>.
<br><br>
<b>20.</b> Go to Butcherblock Mountains and look for the Half Elf Bard named <b>Vedico</b> by the docks.  Give her the Horn and she will hand you a <b>Note for Forpar</b>.
<br><br>
<b>21.</b> Take this Note to <b>Forpar Fizfla</b>.  He then gives you a Note and asks for 3 more items: an Amalgym Tentacle, the Backbone of an Ancient Fishman, and a Petrified Skull of a Lycanthrope.
<br><br>
<b>22.</b> The <b>Amalgym Tentacle</b> is dropped by the <b>Amygdalan Tendril</b> in the Plane of Fear.
<br><br>
<b>23.</b> The <b>Backbone of an Ancient Fishman</b> is dropped by the <b>Phinigel's Spine</b> in Kedge Keep.
<br><br>
<b>24.</b> Finally, the <b>Petrified Skull of a Lycanthrope</b> is dropped by the <b>Drolvarg Warlord</b> in Karnor's Castle.  Its actual name is <b>Petrified Werewolf Skull</b>.
<br><br>
<b>25.</b> Take these 3 items and the Note to Forpar and give them to him.  He will then give you the <b>Lute's Head</b> and the <b>Lute's Neck</b>.  He will then ask for 3 more items: a Large Red Dragon Scale, a Large White Dragon Scale, and 2 Metal Bits.
<br><br>
<b>26.</b> The <b>Large Red Dragon Scale</b> can be any scale from any large red dragon.  <b>Talendor</b> in Skyfire and <b>Nagafen</b> in Solusek B both drop scales that are accepted by Forpar.
<br><br>
<b>27.</b> The <b>Large White Dragon Scale</b> can be any scale from any large white dragon.  <b>Gorenaire</b> in Dreadlands and <b>Lady Vox</b> in Permafrost both drop scales that are accepted by Forpar.
<br><br>
<b>28.</b> The last items are the <b>2 Metal Bits</b>.  These are create by a blacksmith.  These are made with and become trivial with a skill of 21.
<br><br>
<b>29.</b> You are almost done.  You still need the strings for the lute.  These are dropped by <b>Trakanon</b> in Sebilis.  Kill him and loot <b>Trakanon Gut Strings</b>.
<br><br>
<b>30.</b> Done.  Now take the 4 items you collected and give them to <b>Forpar</b>.  He will then reward you with the <b>Lute's Body</b> and the <b>Lute's Strings</b>.
<br><br>
<b>31.</b> You should now have all 4 parts of the Lute, the head, neck, body, and strings.  Give all 4 to Forpar and he will reward you with the <b>Mystical Lute</b>.
<br><br>
<b>32.</b> Return to Dreadlands and look for <b>Baldric Slezaf</b> once again.  Give him the 4 items he previously requested, the Top and Bottom Parts of Page 24, Page 25, and the Mystical Lute.  He will then reward you with the Singing Short Sword.</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Author:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Wraith (Bristlebane)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Quest Reward:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Singing Short Sword</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma"></font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>1H Slashing, Delay: 26, Damage: 16, STR+15, DEX+10, STA+10, CHA+15, HP+50, Mana+10, All Saves+10</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rating:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>3.8</b> (average of <b>70</b> votes)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rate this quest:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"